### 测试VECTOR_ONLY
POST http://localhost:8080/api/rag/search
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "spaceId": 1,
  "query": "异步向量化任务的作用是什么",
  "retrievalMode": "VECTOR_ONLY",
  "topK": 5
}


### 测试KEYWORD_ONLY
POST http://localhost:8080/api/rag/search
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "spaceId": 1,
  "query": "EmbeddingTaskService",
  "retrievalMode": "KEYWORD_ONLY",
  "topK": 5
}

### 测试HYBRID
POST http://localhost:8080/api/rag/search
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "spaceId": 1,
  "query": "EmbeddingTaskService 异步向量化任务",
  "retrievalMode": "HYBRID",
  "topK": 5,
  "candidateK": 20,
  "vectorWeight": 0.7,
  "keywordWeight": 0.3
}


### 测试HYBRID_RERANK
POST http://localhost:8080/api/rag/search
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "spaceId": 1,
  "query": "EmbeddingTaskService 异步向量化任务",
  "retrievalMode": "HYBRID_RERANK",
  "topK": 5,
  "candidateK": 20,
  "vectorWeight": 0.6,
  "keywordWeight": 0.4
}


### 测试ask使用HYBRID_RERANK
POST http://localhost:8080/api/rag/ask
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "spaceId": 1,
  "question": "异步向量化任务的作用是什么？",
  "retrievalMode": "HYBRID_RERANK",
  "topK": 5,
  "candidateK": 20,
  "vectorWeight": 0.6,
  "keywordWeight": 0.4
}

